                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.248/235: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Lauchlin Currie</persName>,
                        Administrative Assistant to President <persName>Roosevelt</persName>, to
                        Madame <persName type="to">Chiang Kai-shek</persName>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="94" xml:id="d757fn1">Copy received in the Department on September
                        6.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-09-05">September 5,
                            1941</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>British have agreed to diversion of 33 Hudsons and 33 DB–7s by end of year.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
